Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，什麼都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保跟清水老師\N竟然是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保你太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師不是結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保也不可能是她老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和有夫之婦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是有夫之婦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜夜春宵的有夫之婦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早不要看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夫之婦指的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟男人結了婚的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是做早操的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先從手部運動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼絲茉茉會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我保管，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的，搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘後要出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師到最後還是沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個到底在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我要這個跟這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛又要託我保管絲茉茉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，手，手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為棒球比賽轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定錄影的節目\N被延後三十分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變設定時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之回背包裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，那台電腦是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保不知道什麼時候\N偷放到我的背包裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要我幫他保管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，幹嘛要我保管呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不會成為包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會妨礙到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但方便、漂亮\N還什麼都會替你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的有很多好處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該對裕美發牢騷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你願意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管牢騷還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都全年無休，照單全收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是新保那傢伙害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再響五聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會轉到答錄機模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有影像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這邊才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，自己接好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師我很高興喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼嗯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟清水老師現在私奔中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在問你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛跟補習班老師私奔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候\N跟她開始交往的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經快半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是\N剛到補習班上課的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在我不注意時跟老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我說了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼重要的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台電視不但是舊型  又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接的方法一定也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我去稔家裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要乖乖看家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是“私奔”？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是壞事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道\N該怎麼回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班學生竟然跟老師私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保這個大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和少爺來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了，發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去準備本須和少爺的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真誇張的出場方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託將她接到有畫面的電話線上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指超高速通信線路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟誰通電話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞私奔的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫面會出現在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上會出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你在國分寺家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛剛的話題，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你說也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把你當作朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也當你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為多香子不同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多香子已經結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次在我那邊過夜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚之後馬上就迷上電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻間的談話\N變得都是電腦的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子以為他只是\N剛買了電腦高興過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也沒在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一段時間之後\N她丈夫就只跟電腦說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多香子在不在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只跟電腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對電腦不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概想不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種人一直在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些話就是指這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離補習班不遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個小公園對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是剛到補習班的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我經過那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還是叫她清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時老師她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在鞦韆上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為她只是童心大發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩玩鞦韆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我吃完晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻還在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為門鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘了帶鑰匙了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙我是有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是上了門鍊，打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門鍊是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好罵他幾句不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她搖了搖頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後我就窮追不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子認為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是補習班學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是補習班老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我說了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就變成了今天這個局面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男性的人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說過我是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管說幾次她還是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次多香子到本須和房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算兩人好好談談的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談談關於我們的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過事到臨頭\N她好像還是害怕了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的心還真是難懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:17:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟誰在通電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟本須和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比平常性感好幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過或許我可以幫上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，新保這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果只能當個商量的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，還是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是到本須和房間去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我找了一個晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我鬧得很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得他很疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像很睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是無意識狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我試著問了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結婚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能喜歡上別人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人，是無法抗拒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喜歡上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有對自己都是痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在其中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然說得出這種大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不知為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡像是放下一塊大石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了更輕鬆自在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要到我身邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒，就是表示快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是無憂無慮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還叫我新保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼問題來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳猜猜\N我一直想要妳怎麼叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖是好人卻沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷上電腦的丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算讓女孩流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是覺得電腦比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:23:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.65,0:24:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更更要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，煮飯」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.57,0:24:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我肚子發出的聲音
